chapters.title: "Mad Max 2: The Road Warrior" (1981) Warner Bros. Pictures
"Mad Max Beyond Thunderdome" (1985) Warner Bros. Pictures
"Mad Max: Fury Road" (2015) Warner Bros. Pictures

description:
On this Mini-Canon, we take a look at a character that gets not one, but... two whole iterations in film: Max Rockatansky, a.k.a Mad Max.
